{{unreferenced|date=January 2017}}
The '''Alterans''' are a fictional race in the [[Stargate]] universe that have been portrayed as the first evolution of the Human form, having later ascended into a state of pure energy. In the timeframe of the television shows, the Alterans are politically divided into two groups; one known primarily as the [[Ori (Stargate)|Ori]], and the other known as the [[Ancient (Stargate)|Ancients]] ([[Stargate SG-1]]), the [[Ancestor (Stargate)|Ancestors]] ([[Atlantis (Stargate)|Atlantis]]), and the [[Lanteans (Stargate)|Lanteans]] ([[Atlantis (Stargate)|Atlantis]]). The Alterans are one of the oldest sentient races known in the Stargate universe, and are also considered to be the most technically advanced race there is.
