arry (composer)|John Barry]] **''[[Séance on a Wet Afternoon]]'' (1964) Produced by **''[[Chaplin (film)|Chaplin]]'' (1992) '''[[Bille August]]''' *[[Hans Zimmer]] **''[[The House of the Spirits (film)|The House of the Spirits]]'' (1993) **''[[Smilla's Sense of Snow (film)|Smilla's Sense of Snow]]'' (1997) *[[Harry Gregson-Williams]] **''[[Smilla's Sense of Snow (film)|Smilla's Sense of Snow]]'' (1997) with Hans Zimmer **''[[Return to Sender (2004 film)|Return to Sender]]'' (2004) '''[[John G. Avildsen]]''' *[[Bill Conti]] **''[[Rocky]]'' (1976) **''[[Slow Dancing in the Big City ]]'' (1978) **''[[The Formula (1980 film)|The Formula]]'' (1980) **''[[Murder Ink]]'' (1980) - They were both involved with this series. **''[[Neighbors (1981 film)|Neighbors]]'' (1981) **''[[The Karate Kid]]'' (1984) **''[[The Karate Kid Part II]]'' (1986) **''[[Happy New Year (1987 film)|Happy New Year]]'' (1987) **''[[For Keeps (film)|For Keeps]]'' (1988) **''[[Lean on Me (film)|Lean on Me]]'' (1989) **''[[The Karate Kid Part III]]'' (1989) **''[[Rocky V]]'' (1990) **''[[8 Seconds]]'' (1994) **''[[Inferno (1999 film)|Inferno]]'' (1999) '''[[Jon Avnet]]''' *[[Thomas Newman]] **''[[Less Than Zero (film)|Less Than Zero]]'' (1987) Produced by **''[[Men Don't Leave]]'' (1990) Produced by **''[[Heat Wave (1990 film)|Heat Wave]]'' (1990) Produced by **''[[Fried Green Tomatoes (film)|Fried Green Tomatoes]]'' (1991) **''[[The War (1994 film)|The War]]'' (1994) **''[[Up Close and Personal (film)|Up Close and Personal]]'' (1996) **''[[Red Corner]]'' (1997) **''[[WIGS (web channel)|WIGS]]'' (2012&ndash;2013) '''[[David Ayer]]''' {{div col|colwidth=22em}} *[[Steven Price (composer)|Steven Price]] **''[[Fury (2014 film)|Fury]]'' (2014) **''[[Suicide Squad (film)|Suicide Squad]]'' (2016) **''[[The Tax Collector]]'' (2019) *[[Graeme Revell]] **''[[Harsh Times]]'' (2005) **''[[Street Kings]]'' (2008) *[[Dave Sardy|David Sardy]] **''[[End of Watch]]'' (2012) **''[[Sabotage (2014 film)|Sabotage]]'' (2014) 